# Company Logos Directory

This folder contains company logo images for the rolling belt on the Placement Highlights page.

## Required Logo Files:
- microsoft.png
- google.png
- amazon.png
- mckinsey.png
- bcg.png
- goldman-sachs.png
- jp-morgan.png
- flipkart.png
- deloitte.png
- ey.png
- kpmg.png
- pwc.png
- accenture.png
- tcs.png
- infosys.png
- wipro.png

## Image Guidelines:
- Format: PNG or JPG
- Size: Recommended 200x100px (will be auto-resized)
- Background: Transparent PNG preferred
- Quality: High resolution for crisp display
- Naming: Use lowercase with hyphens (e.g., jp-morgan.png)

## Usage:
These logos will appear in the horizontal rolling belt at the bottom of the Placement Highlights page with smooth animation and hover effects.
